### MongoDB Location Endpoints
# These endpoints provide paginated access to locations with various filters

# --- Variables ---
@host = http://localhost:8000
@api_key = your_api_key_here
@auth_token = Bearer {{api_key}}

### Get Recent Locations (Page 1)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/mongo/location/recent?page=1
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### Get Recent Locations (Page 2)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/mongo/location/recent?page=2
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### Get Oldest Locations (Page 1)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/mongo/location/oldest?page=1
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### Get Successful Locations (Page 1)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/mongo/location/successful?page=1
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### Get Failed Locations (Page 1)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/mongo/location/failed?page=1
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### Get Pending Locations (Page 1)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/mongo/location/pending?page=1
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### Get Locations by Distance - Nearest First (Page 1)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/mongo/location/by-distance?ascending=true&page=1
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### Get Locations by Distance - Farthest First (Page 1)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/mongo/location/by-distance?ascending=false&page=1
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### Get Locations by Branch - San Francisco (Page 1)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/mongo/location/by-branch?branch=San Francisco&page=1
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### Get Locations by Branch - Oakland (Page 1)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/mongo/location/by-branch?branch=Oakland&page=1
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### Get Locations by Branch - San Jose (Page 1)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/mongo/location/by-branch?branch=San Jose&page=1
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### Get Locations with Fallback Method (Page 1)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/mongo/location/with-fallback?page=1
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### Get Location by ID
GET {{host}}/api/v1/mongo/location/location_id_here
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### Sample Location ID lookup
GET {{host}}/api/v1/mongo/location/67890abcdef1234567890abc
Authorization: {{auth_token}}
